high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter on the right of the stove.
Pick up the gray knife on the counter.
Turn left and go to the counter on the right of the dish washer.
Slice half of the red apple on the counter
Put the knife to the left of the apple.
Pick up a couple of slices of the apple.
Turn around and go to the sink on the left.
Wash the apple slices with water in the sink.
Turn around and go to the trash can between the refrigerator and the counter.
Place the washed apple slice inside the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw away washed slices of apple.

high_descs: Turn and move to the counter space with the toaster, which is to the right of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Carry the knife to stand at the counter just right of the dishwasher.
Use the knife to slice the apple.
Place the knife on the counter to the left of the apple.
Pick up a slice of apple  from the counter.
Turn around and carry the apple slice to the sink.
Place the apple slice in the right side of the sink, turn on the water, and then remove the apple once it has been washed.
Turn left and carry the apple slice to the counter space to the left of the dishwasher.
Place the apple slice in the trash bin next to the counter.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a washed apple slice.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife, close to the edge of the counter, and to the left of the fork, on the counter.
Turn to your left and walk to the counter across from you.
Cut the tomato in the very back, on the counter, into slices.
Place the knife on the back counter, to the left of the tomato.
Pick up the right end, tomato slice on the counter.
Turn around and go to the open sink to your left.
Place the tomato slice in the sink, turn the water on, rinse the tomato, turn the water off, and remove the tomato from the sink.
Turn around and go towards the wall at the end of the kitchen, turning to your right at the refrigerator, then walk to the garbage can on the floor, between the refrigerator and the counter.
Place the tomato in the garbage can, on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a clean tomato slice in the garbage.
